Net-MQTT version 0.01
=====================

Net::MQTT blah blah blah




INSTALLATION

	I use Module::Build to build and install the module.
	To install this module type the following:
	
		perl Build.PL
		./Build
		./Build test
		
	And then as root:
	
		./Build install

	Module::Build is available in the debian package:

		libmodule-build-perl


DEPENDENCIES

	This module requires the Compress::Zlib module. It is available
	as the Debian package libcompress-zlib-perl.
	

